data.description: No HOA! ASSUMABLE LOW RATE! LOW MONTHLIES! Newly updated, centrally located, farmhouse chic gem! Whole home water softener conveys! Sun bathe next to your sparkling blue diving pool and your no maintenance lush green yard complete with privacy hedging! New wood grain tile lines this open concept, 4 bedroom, split primary floor plan! Updated modern lighting combines with the beautiful natural light to highlight your gorgeous white kitchen cabinets &  trendy quartz countertops!  The wood burning fireplace is a stunning focal point to your entertaining space overlooking your large extended covered patio to the pool.  The heavy duty solar system is perfect for people who want to maximize energy savings year round! Located around the corner from ASU West and just minutes away from Westgate Entertainment District, Cardinals Stadium, Tanger Outlets, and up and coming VAI Resort and Mattel Theme Park, which makes this a great property for all buyers and investors!
